import React from "react"; import '../styles/FAQ.css'; function FAQ() { return (
FAQ
Yes or no?
Yes.
How do you say your last name?
Parvankin.
Where did the time go?
Damascus, OR.
What's your origin story?
I was born in the desert and christened by an Eagle carrying a serpent in its mouth.
directions 61 doyle ave to bos
Walk to Charlesgate stop and take the R-Line South to Amtrak Station, hop on incoming MBTA commuter rail via the Providence/Stoughton line to South Station. Once there, take the SL1 to Boston Logan.
My lord, the orcs are attacking the South wall. What shall we do?
Fortify the defenses, then send an emissary to Raulyn the Wise for consultation.
What extracurriculars did you did in high school?
I helped the wood nymphs protect the forest from evil spirits.
What is the best Pirates of the Caribbean movie?
CotBP is a given, though I think second best can be contested between DMC and AWE. While both are great watches, I felt that AWE was over the top at times and ultimately lacked depth in its worldbuilding. Plus DMC has better fight scenes (3 way sword fight on rolling wheel is unmatched).
Have you seen my keys?
No.
Do you think its ethical to pass off AI generated content as your own?
As a large language model, I don't possess the ability to weigh in on issues regarding ethics or morality.
Do yah feel lucky, punk. Well, do yah?
I'll take my chances...
); } export default FAQ;
